sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Operator as TrustyAI Operator<br/>Controller
    participant TrustyAISvc as TrustyAI Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant PVC as PVC Storage
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OSAuth as OpenShift OAuth<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant InferenceSvc as KServe InferenceService<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus

    %% Flow 1: TrustyAI Service Deployment
    User->>K8sAPI: Create TrustyAIService CR<br/>HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>kubeconfig credentials
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch event notification<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create PVC, Deployment, Service, Route<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Resources created
    K8sAPI-->>TrustyAISvc: Pod started
    K8sAPI-->>OAuth: OAuth Proxy started

    %% Flow 2: KServe Inference Logging
    Note over Operator,InferenceSvc: Operator patches InferenceService logger config
    InferenceSvc->>TrustyAISvc: POST /consumer/kserve/v2<br/>HTTP/8080<br/>Inference payload<br/>No Auth
    TrustyAISvc->>PVC: Store inference data<br/>Filesystem
    TrustyAISvc->>TrustyAISvc: Calculate metrics<br/>Internal /q/metrics

    %% Flow 3: External User Access
    User->>Route: HTTPS/443<br/>TLS1.2+ (Route cert)
    Route->>OAuth: Forward to OAuth service<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>TLS1.2+ (service-ca)
    OAuth->>OSAuth: Authenticate user<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+
    OSAuth-->>OAuth: User token validated
    OAuth->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>Check 'get pods' permission<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>OAuth: Authorization result
    OAuth->>TrustyAISvc: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8080<br/>No Auth (internal)
    TrustyAISvc-->>OAuth: Response
    OAuth-->>Route: Response
    Route-->>User: HTTPS Response

    %% Flow 4: Metrics Collection
    Prometheus->>TrustyAISvc: GET /q/metrics<br/>HTTP/80<br/>No Auth
    TrustyAISvc-->>Prometheus: Metrics response<br/>trustyai_spd, trustyai_dir
